<L>__{interior living room boardinghouse night}
<A>__{it is about 3:30 the following evening. helen is sitting in a chair leafing through a magazine. she is dressed to go out. a corner of the dining room can be seen, where mr. and mrs. barley are playing cards with mr. krull. mrs. crockett, the landlady, enters from the hall on her way to the dining room and notices helen.}
