<D>__{personally, i won't go out after dark these days.}
<P>__{(with an attempt at slyness)}
<D>__{but then i'm not courting, am i?}
<A>__{she turns to go on into the dining room and as she does so almost bumps into klaatu who is coming out, having been kibitzing the card game.}
